{"tid":754943,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Lexus IS一問","createTime":"2018-07-24T21:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T04:47:47.000Z","uid":195882,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"363f2faed3d06bc3c6383a52954c5ec0941b5527","tid":754943,"uid":195882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T21:02:38.000Z","msg":"話說小弟攞咗牌半年，keep住揸咗3個月車到，人在外國需要買車代步，個人幾鍾意Lexus is係例嘅，本身打算二手買架15年250 f sports 嘅，但又有朋友話咁不如買200t，咁我自己就上網搵下資料又問下人咁，大概知道200t比起250排放量低，快少少，扭力大啲等等，但又有朋友話揸250駕駛樂趣大啲咁話喎，自問小弟真係完全唔熟，所以上黎問下各位師兄，希望有揸緊或者熟路既師兄解答下，感激不盡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/050138_79b53edd601ea226a99304bfc43fd767.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F050138_79b53edd601ea226a99304bfc43fd767.png&h=eda6b57f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/050142_cfe068a5ce128370e6791e2078eaf059.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F050142_cfe068a5ce128370e6791e2078eaf059.png&h=e351c1f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"851f60e3383f96e6fb1bcd585c651d028e599cc0","tid":754943,"uid":195882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T21:06:27.000Z","msg":"同埋直4turbo同V6又有咩分別同揸上手又點呢？小弟真心唔熟，希望有師兄可以指點下迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28783bb34f38a90a605af6849d5d8c8059ecafb0","tid":754943,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T22:55:16.000Z","msg":"去試下咪知<br />\n個個人要嘅感覺都唔同"},{"pid":"96662144c91d9c61b0fcd296abe7624cc7d74530","tid":754943,"uid":195882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28783bb34f38a90a605af6849d5d8c8059ecafb0","tid":754943,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T22:55:16.000Z","msg":"去試下咪知<br />\n個個人要嘅感覺都唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:33:10.000Z","msg":"唔該師兄，黎緊都會準備試，但都想清楚多少少，安心啲<img 